00:31:14.670 --> 00:31:17.930 align:middle line:84%
So the rules that
govern Planck's field

00:31:17.930 --> 00:31:22.130 align:middle line:84%
are the rules that govern the
Higgs field, the rules that

00:31:22.130 --> 00:31:25.310 align:middle line:84%
govern this field that the
abbot is describing for me.

00:31:25.310 --> 00:31:29.420 align:middle line:84%
Those rules tell us why the
abbot was absolutely correct

00:31:29.420 --> 00:31:33.180 align:middle line:84%
when he said to me that we
must become in our lives

00:31:33.180 --> 00:31:35.550 align:middle line:84%
the things that we choose
to experience in the world.

00:31:35.550 --> 00:31:39.160 align:middle line:90%


00:31:39.160 --> 00:31:41.050 align:middle line:84%
Both the discovery
of the Higgs field

00:31:41.050 --> 00:31:43.810 align:middle line:84%
and the wisdom of the
Tibetan abbot tell us

00:31:43.810 --> 00:31:47.050 align:middle line:84%
that not only are we connected
through a field of energy,

00:31:47.050 --> 00:31:49.160 align:middle line:90%
but we are the field.

00:31:49.160 --> 00:31:50.530 align:middle line:90%
We are the matrix.

00:31:50.530 --> 00:31:52.480 align:middle line:84%
And it's because
we're the matrix

00:31:52.480 --> 00:31:54.430 align:middle line:84%
that the discoveries
that describe it

00:31:54.430 --> 00:31:57.410 align:middle line:84%
are describing us as
well, our possibilities,

00:31:57.410 --> 00:32:00.040 align:middle line:90%
our capabilities, our potential.

